parameters:
Zerachiel: Eden should be waiting beyond
this. I wonder if I'm prepared?

Zerachiel: We'll talk later! Right now,
I'll help you!!

????: I went through a lot of trouble to
obtain the Seventh Curse. I would
appreciate it if you didn't take it
without permission...

Zerachiel: Welcome to the farthest
reaches of the world, the land of all
beginnings.

Zerachiel: I never thought you would
show yourself so boldly.

Star God Eden: You have traveled a long
way to reach here.

Star God Eden: It would be rude not to
show my face.

Zerachiel: There's no need to talk with
you, who deceived me, at this point.

Zerachiel: Now, let's have Effy returned
to me.

Star God Eden: That's a difficult matter
to discuss, Zerachiel.

Star God Eden: The Seventh Curse has the
power to drain one's soul.

Star God Eden: By incorporating the
Seventh Curse that grows in proportion
to the number of souls absorbed...

Star God Eden: I have obtained the power
to unite the world as one.

Zerachiel: T-The power to unite the
world as one...?

Rabi: Such unexpected words have come
out...

Star God Eden: The world you live in and
this world were originally one.

Star God Eden: However, when a giant
meteorite fell, we were isolated in this
world, continent by continent, by the
Emperor of the Ancestors.

Star God Eden: Many countries have
perished, many people have been lost,
and I have also lost most of my power...

Star God Eden: With the Seventh Curse, I
have regained my power and obtained even
more power than I originally had.

Star God Eden: With this power, it is
possible to... obtain the world in my
hands.

Sachia: That is the power of the Seventh
Curse...
Lala: This is not a joke...

Star God Eden: The Seventh Curse is an
amazing power.

Star God Eden: If there is such a
wonderful thing, there is nothing to
fear anymore...!

Star God Eden: By annihilating the
despicable Michelin people and freeing
ourselves from all sources of anxiety,
we can pursue a world exclusively for
the people of Eden!

Star God Eden: Now is the time for me to
obtain everything in the world!

Star God Eden: Truly, it is the paradise
that the gods desired!

Zerachiel: Eden, can I ask you
something?
Zerachiel: Are you happy with that?
Star God Eden: ...And, what about it?
Zerachiel: We are beings of desire.

Zerachiel: There are things I want to do
and things I want to try.

Claudia: If you trace history, every
country has experienced war.

Claudia: We won the war and became a
great nation. But in the end, the
country was destroyed by civil war...

Claudia: Those born from conflict will
perish in conflict.

Star God Eden: To prevent that from
happening, there is the Seventh Curse.

Star God Eden: With this overwhelming
power, we can build an eternal
paradise...

Star God Eden: I am different from a
foolish king.

Sachia: I think even the kings of the
countries that perished had the same
thoughts.
Lala: Actually, I am betraying Eden.

Rabi: There will be more people like
Lala in the future, I suppose.

Star God Eden: In that case, I will just
take care of it.

Star God Eden: To lead to a more
righteous world, together with the
knowledgeable.
Star God Eden: I also have a proposal.

Star God Eden: If you have come this
far, you must understand what is
necessary for the world to come, through
your own experiences.

Star God Eden: Everyone, I want you to
cooperate with my endeavor.

Star God Eden: In order to pioneer a new
era, a fresh perspective is also
necessary.

Star God Eden: If you all cooperate, we
will become an eternal and immortal
existence, ruling over all people.

Star God Eden: It is possible for us to
create an eternal paradise, a new
history, with our own hands.

Star God Eden: Everyone, won't you
witness the dawn together with me?

Zerachiel: I would be troubled if you
forgot the reason why I came here.

Zerachiel: Our goal has always been the
same.
Zerachiel: ...Effy, I came to help you.

Claudia: There is no meaning in
negotiations built upon sacrifice.

Sachia: I don't know Effy, but I
understand that she's suffering.

Rabi: I hate the Star God. I'd rather
die than cooperate.

Lala: I refuse as well. After all,
you'll just betray us again, won't you?

Lala: ...Just like when it was Ern-
sama!!

Star God Eden: ...It's very
disappointing, everyone.

Star God Eden: To defy the gods, you
truly are a lowly Michelin citizen...

Star God Eden: As expected, a failed
creation of a homunculus.

Zerachiel: So, that's your true
intention, Star God.

Star God Eden: The conversation is over,
everyone. We will now transition to the
final phase of the plan.
Star God Eden: Yes, that's right.

Star God Eden: We are just releasing the
power of the Seventh Curse.

Eden: Amazing...! This is the power of
the Seventh Curse...!!

Sachia: The elements... and the souls...
are being sucked in...?
Lala: We won't last long like this...

Eden: Oh my, the wisdom of the evil god
is truly terrifying.

Eden: It is capable of creating even
forbidden things like the Seventh Curse.

Eden: Now, the forbidden curse has been
activated.

Eden: Show me your power, how will you
stand against me!!

Lulu: It's dangerous ahead. Make sure
you're prepared before proceeding.
I want to modify my equipment

Lulu: This is the final battle, do your
best!!

Will you escape to the magical city of
Vaal?
